 雖然而家同左佢一齊但係如果可以早啲就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e2bed7c2c56a42b916caf8bbb64b32404d9089","tid":352422,"uid":60813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T10:12:32.000Z","msg":"梗係主動少少好。女仔要俾明確signal毒撚，咁佢先敢行動。"},{"pid":"d297e2a34993883feef7fb3fd0c270aaf5726ec2","tid":352422,"uid":115082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T10:13:38.000Z","msg":"鍾意靚女"},{"pid":"db71a79bf5c0d5e4e0a173919813d2cf7a8d6237","tid":352422,"uid":128674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T10:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我鍾意個個都係巨蟹仔 好被動阿<br />\n有諗過佢真係星座問題定其實唔鍾意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唉 我會做最壞打算</blockquote><br />\n加油阿絲打"},{"pid":"12fe78fd4095201ddbf593d2f8d9204657c641b0","tid":352422,"uid":72258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T10:36:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好靜 被動 內向 慢熱<br />\n鐘意D 主動、活潑、嘈既女仔 <br />\n起碼可以互補<br />\n如果唔係 2個人都靜又被動好慘 迫自己扮主動又好累<br />\n <br />\n利申 射手男</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都鐘意左個人馬男呀<br />\n不過佢話很多架喎⋯⋯<br />\n佢話忙所以少左覆 到底係咪真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 其實一直都有傾 係呢一兩日無乜"},{"pid":"730b07fc9c485d3163f86f2366d0531fef36ef7b","tid":352422,"uid":80822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好靜 被動 內向 慢熱<br />\n鐘意D 主動、活潑、嘈既女仔 <br />\n起碼可以互補<br />\n如果唔係 2個人都靜又被動好慘 迫自己扮主動又好累<br />\n <br />\n利申 射手男</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n+1，不過我係天蠍男"},{"pid":"d67117e6cad702a4f37ae7994a95c69c09ef9416","tid":352422,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T12:34:46.000Z","msg":"貪你有波咋"},{"pid":"c81cd1a1300e841d42e801ce57aa6fdb05d6e7e8","tid":352422,"uid":131033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:38:56.000Z","msg":